                            	  3215: RTS_011
00:00001AAA 4E75            	  3216: 	RTS
                            	  3217: 
                            	  3218: * do this dimension size (d1) * array data size (Asptl)
                            	  3219: 
                            	  3220: * do a 16 x 32 bit multiply
                            	  3221: * d1 holds the 16 bit multiplier
                            	  3222: * Asptl holds the 32 bit multiplicand
                            	  3223: 
                            	  3224: * d0	bbbb  bbbb
                            	  3225: * d1	0000  aaaa
                            	  3226: *	----------
                            	  3227: * d0	rrrr  rrrr
                            	  3228: 
