00:00002394 CCC3            	  4703: 	MULU.w	d3,d6				* FFFF * DDDD =       rrrr  SSSS
00:00002396 C8C5            	  4704: 	MULU.w	d5,d4				* EEEE * DDDD = QQQQ  rrrr
                            	  4705: 
