00:0000283C B2BCB00F33C7    	  5415: 	CMP.l		#$B00F33C7,d1		* compare mantissa with n*2^7 max
00:00002842 64A6            	  5416: 	BCC.s		LAB_EXOU			* if => go over/underflow
                            	  5417: 
